Red Run is conveniently located in Owings Mills, just moments from I-795 and the Baltimore Beltway in lovely New Town. Please come and take a tour of our brand-new elevator community!

Information.LongDescription: Everyone desires a place to call home. Naturally. When you make yourself at home in the refreshingly classic community of Riverstone at Owings Mills, it is natural you would feel content with life behind closed doors. Riverstone shows like a dream home. The custom-tiled entryway opens into a room where light streams in through abundant windows. Gourmet kitchens and master baths with oval soaking tubs offers endless luxury, comfort and style. Your home should be your solace, a stronghold for everything you love about your life. Riverstone at Owings Mills is the natural choice.

Information.ShortDescription: Welcome to The Estates ! Our property is located in the Heart of Pikesville's Town Center near 695 Beltway, less than one mile from the Area Metro Train for Easy Downtown Travel
Information.LongDescription: The Estates in Pikesville. The Estates will offer you all the comforts of home including a fully equipped modern kitchen, built in microwave. washer/dryer, huge walk-in closets, resort style pool, 24 hour fitness center, an internet caf, and much more. The Estates were built in 1988 but all apartments have been renovated within the last three years. We are a controlled access community that houses 208 apartment homes. Altogether we have 16 buildings that make up the 208 apartment homes. The Estates is a luxury apartment community. Again, we would love to have you here at The Estates as a resident. Should you have any questions or would like to discuss The Estates further, please do not hesitate to give us a call.
Information.DrivingDirections: The Estates is located on Old Court Road in the heart of Pikesvilles Town Center. From Interstate 695, take Exit 20 and turn right onto Reisterstown Road. Continue to Old Court Road and turn right. The Estates will be 1 and 1/2 blocks on the left.

Information.LongDescription: The Sagamore is one of the finest luxury rentals in a long line of great Upper West Side apartments. These elegant pet-friendly Manhattan apartments boast a pre-war look and feel, yet offer a NYC lifestyle that is decidedly twenty-first century. The concierge-attended lobby is finished in wood and marble. The floor plans of these quintessential Upper West Side apartments range from spacious studios to dramatic one and two bedroom residences. Custom finishes include gourmet kitchens with granite countertops and Euro-style cabinetry, pre-war style marble baths, oak parquet floors and customized closets. Select residences offer floor- to-ceiling windows and spacious private terraces. This Upper West Side apartment building also features a childrens playroom, landscaped rooftop sun terrace with BBQ grills and stunning views, entertainment lounge, and a state-of-the-art health and fitness center.
